Package: dm-xor-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dkms, linux-headers-generic | linux-headers
Description: Device-mapper XOR-split target (DKMS)
 Device-mapper target that XOR-splits data across N disks for data
 security through redundant encoding.
 .
 This package provides the dm_xor_mod kernel module via DKMS,
 which will automatically compile and install the module for each
 kernel version installed on the system.
